<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Learning for Vitamin</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/app.css">
</head>

<body>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-9/reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-w1Q4orYjBQndcko6MimVbzY0tgp4pWB4lZ7lr30WKz0vr/aWKhXdBNmNb5D92v7s"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav"
            aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <img class="navbar-brand"
                src="data:image/png;base64,"></img>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                <li class="nav-item active">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#home">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#cars">Cars</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#prices">Prices</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#favcar">Favorite car</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <h2 id="home" class="ml-5">Short story</h2>
    <p class="ml-5">In the last years, my passion for cars has truly taken off, and among my favorite vehicles, the
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Porsche_992">Porsche 992</a>, <a
            href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BMW_M8">Bmw M8</a>,
        and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dodge_Challenger">Dodge Challenger</a> have become iconic choices for
        me.
    </p>
    <h2 class="h2center mb-4"><a href="http://localhost:3000/cars" class="h2center mb-4" id="cars">All Cars</a></h2>
    <section class="pb-4">
        <% cars.forEach(function(car) { %>
            <div class="card mb-2">
                <img src="<%= car.imageUrl %>" class="card-img-top" alt="<%= car.brand %> <%= car.model %>">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="bg-info list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span class="font-weight-bold">Car:</span>
                            <span>
                                <%= car.brand %>
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="bg-info list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span class="font-weight-bold">Model:</span>
                            <span>
                                <%= car.model %>
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="bg-info list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span class="font-weight-bold">Engine:</span>
                            <span>
                                <%= car.engine %>
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="bg-info list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span class="font-weight-bold">Horse Power:</span>
                            <span>
                                <%= car.horsepower %>
                            </span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
    </section>


    <h2 class="h2center mb-4" id="prices">Prices</h2>
    <section class="pb-4">
        <div class="cardPrice mb-2">
            <h2>Porsche</h2>
            <ol>
                <li class="price">
                    The 2022 992 911 Turbo S price is $216,100. The price of the 992 911 Turbo S for sale is slightly
                    higher than the 992 Turbo MSRP of $182,900. The 992 Turbo S Cabriolet (also called the 992 Turbo S
                    Cab) starts at $228,900.</li><br>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="cardPrice mb-2">
            <h2>BMW</h2>
            <ol>
                <li class="price">The BMW M8 Convertible has a RRP range of £145,090 to £166,090. However, with carwow
                    you
                    can save on average £12,166. Prices start at £133,764 if paying cash. The price of a used BMW M8
                    Convertible on carwow starts at £98,913.</li><br>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="cardPrice mb-2">
            <h2>Dodge</h2>
            <ol>
                <li class="price">The 2023 Dodge Challenger starts at $30,545 for the base SXT trim. The R/T trim is
                    your
                    ticket into the V8 club and starts at $39,385, while 807 horsepower can be yours for as little as
                    $83,650. But most buyers stick with something under the $50,000 mark.</li><br>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="favcar" class="pb-4">
        <div class="cardFav mb-2">
            <h2> Tell me your favorite car</h2>

            <form action="https://www.google.com/search">
                <div>
                    <label for="car">Check if this is your favorite car:</label>
                </div>
                <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Car" id="carInput" required><br>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-info" id="searchBtn">Search</button>
            </form>
            <form id="carForm" action="/cars" method="post">
                <div class="car">
                    <div>
                        <label for="car">Enter a car: </label><br>
                        <input type="text" id="car" name="brand" placeholder="Car" required>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="model">Enter a model: </label><br>
                        <input type="text" id="model" name="model" placeholder="Model" required>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="engine">Enter an engine: </label><br>
                        <input type="text" id="engine" name="engine" placeholder="Engine" required>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="hp">Enter horse power: </label><br>
                        <input type="text" id="hp" name="horsepower" placeholder="HP" required>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="imageUrl">Enter a link for photo: </label><br>
                        <input type="text" id="imageUrl" name="imageUrl" placeholder="Photo link" required>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-info">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="index.js"></script>

</body>

</html>